{"word":"G1494 - εἰδωλόθυτον - eidōlóthyton - i-do-loth'-oo-ton - Offered to idols","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰδωλόθυτον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eidōlóthyton</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">i-do-loth'-oo-ton</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Offered to idols</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"விக்கிரகங்களுக்குப் படைத்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"sacrificed to idols"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1497 - εἴδωλον - eídōlon - i'-do-lon/1497\">G1497</a> and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2380 - θύω - thýō - thoo'-o/2380\">G2380</a>; an <i>image sacrifice</i>, that is, part of an <i>idolatrous offering:</i> - (meat, thing that is) offered (in sacrifice, sacrificed) to (unto) idols.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1493/1493\">G1493</a>, <a href=\"#/G1494/1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G1495/1495\">G1495</a>, <a href=\"#/G1496/1496\">G1496</a>, <a href=\"#/G1497/1497\">G1497</a>, <a href=\"#/G2405/2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406/2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407/2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409/2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411/2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412/2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413/2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416/2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417/2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2418/2418\">G2418</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420/2420\">G2420</a>, <a href=\"#/G2712/2712\">G2712</a>, <a href=\"#/G749/749\">G749</a>"}]}